USA and the Baja California Peninsula, Mexico, by limiting
either: (a) tissue nitrogen uptake and storage by adult
sporophytes during periods of elevated temperature, and/or (b)
production of embryonic sporophytes by microscopic gametophytes.
Results suggest that while adult sporophytes of both species are
